lyrics:
Bachche hain masoom,
Aur dil se pyare,
Unki hansi se khilte hain,
Sabke chehre nayaare.

(Chorus)

Bachche hain khushiyon ka,
Ek anmol tohfa,
Unki muskurahat se milta hai,
Jeevan ko jeene ka sahara.

(Verse 2)

Bachche hain khelne ke,
Aur masti karne ke,
Unke sath ho jaate hain,
Sabhi gam bhul jaane ke.

(Chorus)

Bachche hain khushiyon ka,
Ek anmol tohfa,
Unki muskurahat se milta hai,
Jeevan ko jeene ka sahara.

(Bridge)

Bachche hain bhavishya ke,
Ek ujjwal sitare,
Unki kiranon se roshan hoga,
Duniya ka har ek kinara.

(Chorus)

Bachche hain khushiyon ka,
Ek anmol tohfa,
Unki muskurahat se milta hai,
Jeevan ko jeene ka sahara.

(Outro)

Bachche hain khushiyon ka,
Ek anmol tohfa,
Unki muskurahat se milta hai,
Jeevan ko jeene ka sahara.
